{"tid":110840,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[完全無人理]  Android Wear 2.0 將於 2 月 9 日推出更新名單曝光","createTime":"2017-02-07T04:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T21:30:49.000Z","uid":51717,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fea06810a8e5c4df4ff802108c93bd1b078d9d63","tid":110840,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:00:54.000Z","msg":"Android Wear 2.0 將於 2 月 9 日推出更新名單曝光<br />\n<br />\n有關 Google 的 Android Wear 2.0 系統已經傳聞了好一段時間，只可惜在多個開發者預覽版本面世之後，正式版本的推出時間卻一再被延遲。幸好來到今日終於有一個好消息，因為爆料大神 @evleaks 表示 Android Wear 2.0 將會於 2 月 9 日推出，而 LG 兩款新智能手錶將會成為最先採用的新產品。<br />\n<br />\n留意上星期有報導指 Google 已經通知開發者即將會更新至 Android Wear 2.0，以便他們可以提前做好準備去更新各款應用程式。除推出日期外，@evleaks 更表示 Android Wear 2.0 會率先登陸 LG Watch Sport 及 LG Watch Style 這兩款全新智能手錶。據了解兩款新錶皆會採用圓形 OLED 熒幕、4GB 儲存、Wi-Fi 及藍牙等，而 Sport 版更會具備心跳感應器、GPS 及支援 LTE 網絡。<br />\n<br />\n不過報導同時亦指出由於 LG Watch Sport 及 LG Watch Style 可能要等到 2 月尾舉行的 MWC 2017 才會發表，因此預計最快要 3 月才購買得到。至於舊產品方面，一般相信各款旗艦級智能手錶都可更新至 Android Wear 2.0，而網上亦已經流出相關名單，比如 Moto 360 及 LG G Watch Urbance 等都榜上有名，但數量不算太多只得 18 款。<br />\n<br />\n‧Moto 360 (2nd Gen.)<br />\n‧Moto 360 Sport<br />\n‧LG Watch Urbane 2nd Edition LTE<br />\n‧LG Watch Urbane<br />\n‧LG G Watch R<br />\n‧Polar M600<br />\n‧Casio Smart Outdoor Watch<br />\n‧Nixon Mission<br />\n‧Tag Heuer Connected<br />\n‧Fossil Q Wander<br />\n‧Fossil Q Marshal<br />\n‧Fossil Q Founder<br />\n‧Michael Kors Access Bradshaw Smartwatch<br />\n‧Michael Kors Access Dylan Smartwatch<br />\n‧Huawei Watch<br />\n‧Huawei Watch Ladies<br />\n‧Asus ZenWatch 2<br />\n‧Asus ZenWatch 3<br />\n<br />\n來源：Twitter（@evleaks）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/01/18/android-wear-2-0-launches-on-feb-9/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F01%2F18%2Fandroid-wear-2-0-launches-on-feb-9%2Flife-tech%2Fwatch-wireless-home%2F&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=11e0d93a\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/01/18/android-wear-2-0-launches-on-feb-9/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/</a>"},{"pid":"88d947ef35e894e3571f23e6eec72d3cc1c06418","tid":110840,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:11:39.000Z","msg":"仲有兩日"},{"pid":"e0d19ffcb945aa5ff3810b0966ba07970c5cb055","tid":110840,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f80732a993c5d613435de33c58de4d331d1e93b","tid":110840,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:08:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.gsmarena.com/exclusive_photos_of_lg_watch_style_leaked-news-23215.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gsmarena.com%2Fexclusive_photos_of_lg_watch_style_leaked-news-23215.php&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=854c7e2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gsmarena.com/exclusive_photos_of_lg_watch_style_leaked-news-23215.php</a><br />\n傳&nbsp;LG Watch Style用240 mAh battery，冇3G, 4G, GPS or NFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce83825044e16bd86e7778edc69b49e9a667695","tid":110840,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.gsmarena.com/exclusive_photos_of_lg_watch_style_leaked-news-23215.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gsmarena.com%2Fexclusive_photos_of_lg_watch_style_leaked-news-23215.php&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=854c7e2d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gsmarena.com/exclusive_photos_of_lg_watch_style_leaked-news-23215.php</a><br />\n傳&nbsp;LG Watch Style用240 mAh battery，冇3G, 4G, GPS or NFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLG Watch Style 無心跳計乜柒都無，美金250即係港幣成2000蚊<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":